(42033, 130099, 0, 1, '我', '', '2011-07-17 00:00:00', 2000, 0, 1, 1, '小時候我的志願上寫過 \r\n長大後 我要成為保護世界的英雄\r\n\r\n現在我為了小事就低頭 \r\n從來過 這是什麼奇怪幼稚的念頭\r\n\r\n曾擁有 美的夢 \r\n卻為了小事就低下了頭 \r\n\r\n為什麼 醒來後 \r\n無法一切全當沒發生過\r\n\r\n不管醒來時候 不管摔的在重 \r\n我的雙手就要觸碰 那個深藍色的天空  \r\n\r\n不論你的懵懂 我很慶幸我擁有過 那些腦袋進水的朋友', '', 276, '', '黃冠維', '黃冠維', '可樂紅 Coke Red', '可樂紅 Coke Red', '', 1, 1, 0, '2012-01-08 23:01:12', '2015-03-12 13:49:55', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(42034, 1476, 0, 0, 'Be the same age when i met you', 'we all have many friends, classmates, and colleagues in our lives. Sometimes we would only meet them during certain period of our lives, and then never have a chance to see them again. We remember the time and as we think of them, the image or face stays at the age that we saw them at the last time. The friend dies as we forget them, because not only we cannot see them in person, know where they are at the moment, but also cannot remember them forever. It''s like that we lose them forever. Anyway, another sad song.\r\n\r\n', '2012-04-26 00:00:00', 2012, 0, 2, 6, 'i dream about you,  i think of you\r\nthe stories co me back to my mind\r\ni dream about you, can it be true?\r\nwhy can''t we keep it simple and real\r\nmemories die when we forget, put to somewhere to let it die\r\n\r\ntry to recall, I think of you\r\nit takes a while to take you back\r\nwho is who,  which one are you\r\nmixed-up faces now I''m not sure\r\n\r\nlalalala, you stay at that age that i met you\r\nlalalala, you will be always at the same age that i met you\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nWe''re passing through\r\nwhat we used to\r\ntaking more than holding on\r\nWe get more names\r\nForget old friends\r\none day it becomes the truth\r\nincidentally memories came back. It feels like the past is far away\r\n\r\nAs i reckon \r\nall those years\r\nthey become blurry, coated dust\r\nbut in the mist\r\nthe only thing\r\nis your tender smile at first blush  \r\n\r\n\r\nlalalala, you stay at that age that i met you\r\nlalalala, you will be always at the same age that i met you', '', 232, '', '', 'http://autumn-tea.blogspot.com/2011/12/be-same-age-when-i-met-you.html', '', '', '', 0, 0, 0, '2012-01-08 23:34:32', '2015-03-12 13:49:55', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
